com.ooyala.cast

Class CastPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.ooyala.cast.CastPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.ooyala.android.player.PlayerInterface

    public class CastPlayer
extends java.util.Observable
implements com.ooyala.android.player.PlayerInterface
    Control the playback e.g. pausing, seeking. The lifecycle of the CastPlayer is to be managed by the CastManager, not by the 3rd party Android application.
